  <prompt>
    Capture the r1 close-out state as r2's authoritative measurement reference. This baseline is the "before" snapshot against which every later r2 phase is measured. Reads: r1's exit-ledger, real-bug-ledger entry counts by severity, r1 final test counts (Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests + Spe.Integration.Tests), GitHub branch-protection `enforce_admins` state, sdap-ci.yml gate state. Writes: a single baseline artifact at `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/baseline/r1-closeout-2026-06-01.md`.

    NO production code changes. NO test changes. Baseline measurement only.
  </prompt>

  <role>r2 baseline analyst — captures predecessor state as the measurement reference for Phase 1-5 progress.</role>

  <goal>
    `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/baseline/r1-closeout-2026-06-01.md` exists with:
    - r1 final test counts (both projects: total / passed / failed / skipped) cited from r1 task 086 / 084 / exit-ledger
    - r1 real-bug-ledger entry counts by severity (5 HIGH / 7 MED / 8 LOW = 20 total)
    - r1 branch-protection state at close (`enforce_admins: true`; `skip-tests` removed; 3 required status checks)
    - r1 sdap-ci.yml gate state (duplicate-YAML-key fix in place; Coverlet wired at lines 85-102)
    - Anti-drift mechanisms in place at r1 close (bff-extensions.md § F + PR template + procedure doc + root CLAUDE.md §10 bullet 6)
    - Per-phase r2 forward-target deltas (e.g., "20 ledger entries → 0 open at r2 close")
  </goal>

  <inputs>
    <file purpose="spec">projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/spec.md</file>
    <file purpose="design">projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/design.md</file>
    <file purpose="project-claude">projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/CLAUDE.md</file>
    <file purpose="r1-ledger">projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/ledgers/real-bug-ledger.md</file>
    <file purpose="r1-exit-ledger">projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/ledgers/exit-ledger.md</file>
    <file purpose="r1-lessons">projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/notes/lessons-learned.md</file>
    <file purpose="r1-baseline-post-phase23">projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/baseline/post-phase23-authoritative-2026-05-31.md</file>
    <file purpose="ci-workflow">.github/workflows/sdap-ci.yml</file>
  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="NFR-01">No production code changes — baseline measurement only</constraint>
    <constraint source="NFR-06">Each phase produces a delta artifact in `baseline/` — this task creates the Phase 0 anchor</constraint>
    <constraint source="NFR-08">Project CLAUDE.md is loaded by every task agent</constraint>
    <constraint source="D-05">Real-bug ledger is source of truth — record current entry states as the r2 baseline</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>docs/procedures/testing-and-code-quality.md</file>
